---
description: Service layer — business logic and database access
globs:
  - src/services/**
---

Services contain all business logic and DB queries.
- Import `server-only` at the top
- Use `db.prepare().run/get/all()` — never raw string concatenation
- API keys are encrypted in DB — use `getApiKeyForUser()` from `apiKey.service.ts`
- Database is `better-sqlite3` in WAL mode at `user_data/history/history.db`
- Settings use key-value store in `settings.service.ts` with typed `DEFAULTS`
- File storage goes to `/uploads/` via `storage.service.ts` — sanitize all filenames

Exemplar: `src/services/database.service.ts`
